          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 792,
          "content": "Laquisha, 16, described being sent to Darwin youth detention 1,500km from home. Twelve minute phone calls. Two hour waits between calls. No family there.\n\nWhen she was asked why young people get in trouble, she answered in one word: oppression.",
          "lineHeight": 1.22,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 34,
          "fontWeight": "500"
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
